Name: Cell HD: emergence
About the game: Against the 'smart germs' of tomorrow's biowarfare, nanites will be our drone soldiers, but for how long? Enter the fluid living world of Cell (built from 'dynamic voxels') to witness the emergence of new life: YOU, a nanobot who shoots deadly colloids, builds defenses and supercharged weapons, deciphers enemy nanotech -- and, by design, learns.
